description:
Watch Sabina K. (2015) Full Movie on Vision Video

Sabina, a divorced mother of two small children, falls in love with Sasa, an old friend from the Bosnian war. The two plan to marry, but Sasa disappears mysteriously. A few weeks later, Sabina discovers that she is pregnant, loses her job, and is threatened by her ex-husband. At her breaking point, she checks into a hotel and begins swallowing pills, slipping into unconsciousness. What happens next is subject to opinion, but one thing is clear—Sabina will never be the same. Inspired by a true story. Viewer discretion advised due to mature themes.

Director: Cristobal Krusen
Starring: Alena Dzebo, Ana Andelic, Mugdim Avdagic
